news_header: Tokmann and Spar are partnering to enhance grocery offerings in Finland.
news_text: Tokmann is collaborating with Spar to challenge the grocery market in Finland, starting this year. The partnership will see Spar's brand integrated into Tokmanni stores, which will expand their fresh product sales. Tokmann aims to establish a new food chain, competing against major players like Kesko, S-Group, and Lidl, who currently dominate over 90% of the market. The first Spar food department is set to open next summer, with plans for more stores and potential independent Spar locations in the future.
